Updates the position of any child to current canvas.   <p>For example: <pre>
 var lbl:Label = new Label();
 lbl.text = &quot;Last Month&quot;;
 canvas.addChild(lbl);
 canvas.updateDataChild(lbl,&quot;Feb&quot;,200);
 </pre> </p>
